# AI Sentiment Analyzer

## Project Overview

AI Sentiment Analyzer is a Python-based application that uses Natural Language Processing (NLP) to determine the sentiment of a given text. The application analyzes user input and classifies it as **Positive**, **Negative**, or **Neutral** based on its sentiment polarity using the TextBlob library.

