## Project Scope

The objective of this project is to:
- Perform sentiment analysis on text.
- Classify text into Positive, Negative, or Neutral categories.
- Demonstrate the basics of Natural Language Processing (NLP).
- Provide a simple AI-based Python application for beginners.
- Serve as an educational and internship project.

